# API Docs Required (Mandatory)

API documentation is part of the deliverable, not follow-up work.

## Same-PR requirement

- Any API endpoint addition, removal, or contract change must include docs updates in the same PR.
- Documentation location: `backend/docs/api/*`.

## Required endpoint documentation fields

- Endpoint and method
- Purpose and business context
- Request format: headers, params, query, and body schema
- Response format: success and error status codes with payload schemas
- Example request payload
- Example response payload

## Release rule

- Do not approve or merge API-affecting PRs without updated docs.
